reviewText: clear wish more hits were included but I understand what the producer was trying to do is make this a new collection of songs with some oldies appeal.  Not a greatest hits collection
Perhaps I like a brighter, more equalized sound.

This Blu-ray contains 14 tracks, recorded live, but without an audience. This disc from the AIX label is one in a series aiming to present the music in the highest sound quality possible. 14 hits from the artist in best sound quality available. Highly recommended.

Siegfried

This is another excellent production from Aix Records, care of Mark Waldrep and company. They produce some of the finest recordings, by great artists old and young, to the highest technical standards available.

I recommend this item to everybody who enjoys good pop with a country tinge and who also values top sonic and visual content.

Mark Waldrep; you do music lovers a great service!

If you are a fan of RITA COOLIDGE and state of the art audio recording then this is a must have BLU-RAY DISC.  Though its in 3D  you can close your eyes
and it is still a dream.
